properties.text:
- To plot a 3D graph, enter its f(x, y) into the calculator and then press [PLT]
- [EX1] through [EX6] are example plots
- Move the calculator by dragging its screen
- Click and drag outside to move the graph
- Scroll moves closer or further away
- [SUN/MOON] button changes the theme
- [?] button toggles this tutorial
